\f1\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 HDEC2000 unit has four regulation (operating) modes called FCR, AVR, VAR and PF mode. One regulation mode is selected depending on the combination of digital input(s) and configuration parameters. 
\f1\fs24 \

